### Welcome to My project log!
Since I eventually have to start documenting things, I figured this might be a good way to do it. So, here goes! 

Currently my only really active project is my arduino-powered servo controller. The current "stable" data for this is located at [tekdemo.github.com/project-sir-vo](tekdemo.github.com/project-sir-vo) , and I'll keep the log in [projects](projects).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
